query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machine_webhook_logs (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  webhookConfigId INT NOT NULL,
  triggerType VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  triggerDataId INT,
  requestPayload TEXT,
  responseStatus INT,
  responseBody TEXT,
  responseTime INT,
  attempt INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  status ENUM('pending', 'success', 'failed', 'retrying') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending',
  errorMessage TEXT,
  triggeredAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  completedAt TIMESTAMP NULL
)
